address="/ledd/2/punkt/1/ledd/1/punkt/9/" id="ledd-2-punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-9"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/1/ledd/1/punkt/9/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-9-ledd-1">§ 3 nåværende nr. 2, 3 og 4 omnummereres til nr. 3, 4 og 5.</article></article></li></ul></article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1">Kapittel II Brannslokking<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Endring av § 10 overskriften og § 10 nr. 1 og nr. 2</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Endring av § 11</article></article></li></ul></article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/3/" id="ledd-2-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1">Kapittel V Alarm- og internkommunikasjon<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/3/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/3/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Endring av § 22 overskriften</article></article></li></ul></article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-1">Nytt <i>Kapittel VI Gassdeteksjon, Nødavstengning</i> innføres.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2">Kapittelet inneholder bestemmelser vedrørende:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-1-ledd-1">gassrisiko/arrangement</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/2/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1">gassdeteksjon</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/3/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1">nødavstengning</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/4/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-1">operasjon og beredskap</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/5/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1">vedlikehold av eksplosjonssikkert utstyr</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/6/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-6"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/2/punkt/6/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-2-punkt-6-ledd-1">utstyr som tas ombord</article></article></li></ul></article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1">Nytt kapittel VII (tidligere kapittel VI). Forskjellige bestemmelser<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Ny § 30 (tidligere § 24) endring i nr. 1 første ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">§ 30 nr. 1 nytt annet ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Nåværende §§ 25, 26 og 27 omnummereres til §§ 31, 32 og 33</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/4/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">Ny § 33 (tidligere § 27) nytt annet ledd</article></article></li></ul></article></article></li></ul></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/" id="ledd-3">Forskriftens kapittel VI trer i kraft 22. mai 1990 for nye innretninger. Eksisterende innretninger skal oppfylle kravene i kapittel VI innen 1. januar 1991.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/4/" id="ledd-4">Forskriftsendringen vil bli innarbeidet i forskriften av 31. januar 1984 nr. 227 og deretter bli inntatt i Sjøfartsdirektoratets forskriftssamling «Regler for flyttbare innretninger» og omtalt i Meddelelser fra Sjøfartsdirektoratet. Den kan fås ved henvendelse til Sjøfartsdirektoratet, Ekspedisjonen, Postboks 8123 Dep., 0032 Oslo 1.</article></main></body></html>